From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*mV-nar|t=to suffer}}.

Cognate with {{cog|bo|མནར||to suffer; suffering}}, and possibly (via homophonous root merger) also {{cog|my|နာ||to suffer pain, to be ill}}.

